import React from 'react' import styles from './Current.module.css' const CurrentWeather = ({current,unixFormatter}) => (

{current.weather[0].description}

{ current && current.main.temp} °C

Wind: {current.wind.speed} m/s

Sunrise: {unixFormatter(current.sys.sunrise,'HH:MM')} AM

Sunset: {unixFormatter(current.sys.sunset,'HH:MM')} PM

) export default CurrentWeather
